%%{init: {"theme": "neutral"}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as Teen (mobile app)
    participant G as API Gateway
    participant AI as AI service
    participant TR as Tracking service
    participant GM as Google Gemini 2.5 Flash
    participant DB as ai_db

    U->>G: POST /api/v1/ai/send { message } (Bearer JWT)
    G->>AI: forward
    AI->>AI: verify JWT locally → resolve profileId
    AI->>TR: GET /internal/v1/tracking/context/{profileId}<br/>(Docker network only — blocked at the gateway)
    TR-->>AI: recent context: moods, sleep, journal summary
    AI->>AI: build prompt = system persona + tracking context<br/>+ conversation history + new message
    AI->>GM: generateContent (API key)
    GM-->>AI: grounded reply
    AI->>DB: persist user message + reply<br/>(chat_sessions / chat_messages)
    AI-->>U: reply that references the user's actual week
